item.title: 44phantom - all figured out
item.description:
…*

I ran last night
Trying to save myself from you
But I was too afraid to lose
And caved in
I thought
You might
Want to hear from me again
I know it’s been awhile since
We last talked
But I heard you’re doing great
Inside some wonderful place
You’re doing everything you said you would

And you got it all figured out
From the way you take control
To the way you’re letting go
You got it all figured out
and I guess it’s all the same
You didn’t need me anyway

It’s not your fault
And we know it never was
I was caught up in a rush
To get out
I blame myself
For everything that you’ve become
And it’s not bad it’s just too much
For me..
But I heard you’re doing great
Inside some wonderful place
You’re doing everything you said you would

And you got it all figured out
From the way you take control
To the way you’re letting go
You got it all figured out
And I guess it’s all the same
You didn’t need me anyway

Don’t ever say I didn’t try
everything to change your mind
I just know now what’s important to you

and If I had another chance
I’d still do it all again
even if it meant that I would still lose

But I heard you’re doing great
Inside some wonderful place
You’re doing everything you said you would…

And you got it all figured out
From the way you take control
To the way you’re letting go
You got it all figured out
and I guess it’s all the same
You didn’t need me anyway

And you got it all figured out
From the way you take control
To the way you’re letting go
You got it all figured out
and I guess it’s all the same
You didn’t need me anyway
Cause you got it all

…*
